questionTitle:
What is the output of the following code?
```cpp
int x = 5;
cout << x++ << " " << x;
```

What is the output of the following C++ code?
```cpp
int x = 5;
cout << x--;
```

What is the output?
```cpp
int x = 5;
int* ptr = &x;
*ptr = 10;
cout << x;
```

